reviewText: I ordered this with another one since my grandchildren realy enjoy the series!!  I liked that it was safely packaged and arrived when needed!
This series is great for the boys but the girls also like it, the story lines are good it teaches respect for things and people, has been played quite alot.
This is the CGI version of Bob and despite that drawback, it was still lots of fun for my little one.
It reminds of real diggers, real dump trucks, real cement mixers, real steamrollers, real cranes, real cherry pickers real building sites

This was a fun addition to the Bob the Builder series and were episodes that I had not seen before. I always have enjoyed this series due to the great relationships and friendship messages that it promotes overall and these episodes were no different! The DVD is well put together and as always the artwork is flawless! I highly recommend this DVD to one and all!
My grandchildren loved watching the movie!
My son loves anything Bob the Builder & this DVD does not dissapoint! Great lessons about being helpful & getting along with others.
OUR FAVORITE SO FAR, WE LOVE BOB BOB BOB..........WE EVEN HAVE HIS PJ'S NOW, 2 PAIRS.
My son loves it and watches it over and over again!!!
Plays great, great picture, no pauses for buffering. My 3 year old son loves watching Bob the Builder. I am very happy that this is offered through my prime membership.
Bob the Builder is an excellent, wholesome kids show. Besides that, claymation is off the hizzy!!!
I think it is a knock off dvd. It plays horribly especially through the theme song. We were very disappointed.

Great DVD, my 3 year old loves it. No complaints! Not much to say about it other then it was as expected and arrived quickly and has been a hit!
Purchased this for my nephews.  My brother reports back that the kids are quiet for up to 5 minutes at a time in the car.  This is considered a great success.

My boy always enjoy watching it.

My 5 year old son absolutely loves Bob the Builder.  It is so cute and it teaches him a lot about construction and different types of vehicles.  It inspires him to be creative.  He will watch the show and then go out in the backyard with his trucks and try to create what he was being taught.

Bob is a wise man. He is a hard workIng American that takes his job seriously. It is refreshing to see a white man doing labor when so many Mexicans are out there taking our jobs. Stay strong, Bobby boy!
